title: Need Graphic Designer (Logo)
body:
Looking for a graphic designer for my new website, please comment if your interested below with a little message and your skype username or a way of contacting you [Looking for someone who will do it for free] 

Thanks!

replies.body: Hey, just wondering what you needed done? I'm a bit of a graphic designer but studying media in uni. You can contact my skype, Matt.Wrap if you want to let me know what you need done :)
